data.description: This home in the community of Lindsford offers tons of amenities such as Basketball, Bike/Jog paths, Bocce, Clubhouse, Community Pool & Spa, Excercise room, Fishing pier, Tennis courts, underground utilities and more.  Centrally located in Fort Myers, near work centers, shopping, medical facilities entertainment and more.  This home site on one of the larges lots in the community and is over 1/2 acre.  This 4 bed/ 2 bath home features plank tile flooring a great room plan off the kitchen, a screened lanai and large windows and sliders overlooking the back yard.  The master bedroom is located just off the great room with yard views and a walk in closet.  Master bath has granite counter tops with dual sinks, and a glass and tile shower.  The kitchen features dark wood cabinets, a walk-in pantry, stainless steel appliances, an island with breakfast bar.  A large dining area is just off the kitchen.  The great room is sunny and bright with large doors to the screen lanai with huge back yard view. Lindsford has so much to offer for family enjoyment and relaxing.
